creator: DiPocket Limited
descriptionHtml:
Better than a bank current account, your PlayIT Card account gives you full control of your daily spend while offering great savings:
• use your PlayIT card everywhere Mastercard is accepted - in store, for e-commerce, for cash withdrawals,
• topup your account with bank transfers to your dedicated bank account number or via a card issued by another bank,
• manage your budget safely - you can only spend the money available on your card,
• receive instant push notifications and easily view transaction history,
• send and request money from friends and family - instantaneously,
• split restaurant and other bills without the hassle of using cash and change,
• control where you card can be used - for that extra bit of peace of mind,
• save on foreign currency transactions when you are abroad. . . . and on cash withdrawal fees in Hungary,
• enjoy the great offers with the dedicated Mastercard Priceless Specials and,
• if you are aged 14-18, make this your first current account - enjoy the independence while staying safe and keeping your parents comfortable as they see know how you spend your money.
And, we almost forgot to mention, show off your cool XBOX branded black card!
P.S.: Your PlayIT account is provided by DiPocket Limited, a company authorized and supervised by the UK Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) as an Electronic Money Institution (#900439). Your money is held in Hungary, with a leading international bank.

This release brings many improvements under the hood, and a handful of bug fixes.
